title: DAZ3D - Tween Ryan 7 Pro Bundle
description:
TWEEN RYAN PRO BUNDLE
---------------------

Including Template files where applicable, this bundle includes:


Challenger Poses for Tween Ryan 7
---------------------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/34698fa01c852f712206d891f607273f.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/33055

20 warrior poses for your favorite Tween Ryan 7 fighter!


Everyday Casual Outfit for Genesis 3 Male
-----------------------------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/6d5271df12481a29d970650e1d2b756d.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/33535

Everyday Casual Outfit for Genesis 3 Male(s)


FWSA Gabriel HD for Tween Ryan 7
--------------------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/92872f7dd927ed4e3a0a21dfd0fd4c6c.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/32975

Gabriel is a high quality character for Tween Ryan 7 for use in DAZ Studio. The head and body for Gabriel are uniquely custom sculpted in Zbrush, and the skin was created using high quality photo references for depth and detail. He also comes with a Sticky Out Ears option, that can be applied to whatever intensity you prefer.


FWSA Max for Tween Ryan 7
-------------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/409aa0debc10e7a57687aaf40c92ce33.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/32505

Max is a high quality character for Tween Ryan 7 for use in Daz Studio 4.8 and up. The head and body are uniquely custom sculpted in Zbrush, and the skin was created using high quality photo references for depth and detail. He comes with two face textures, plain and freckled as well as three different brow colors for each version. Furthermore he also comes with a dirt L.I.E. option that can simply be applied to him to dirty him up. This will work on ALL Genesis 3 Male characters, as well as on Genesis 3 Female. So now you can add a bit of dirty to all your male and female characters. Please Note: While Max was designed with Daz Studio 4.8 (and up) in mind, and its amazing Iray render engine, He will also work and look great using the 3Delight render engine!

Tween Ryan 7
------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/187e3adce1702a052a9a7f5930af462f.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/31783

Tween Ryan 7 is the boy of endless summer. Bicycles, treehouses, scraped elbows and secret handshakes. Hide the matches and keep an eye on the cake in the fridge. School's out!


Tyler Hair for Genesis 2 & 3 Male
---------------------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/8ebe4650cb641425c022c5e4c7c709c2.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/33505

Tyler Hair is a morphing, polygonal model of a grown out brush cut or Ivy League cut. The hair is fitted to Genesis 2 & 3 Male(s) (.DUF) with auto-conforming custom morphs for Daz Original characters. Iray and 3Delight material presets for various texture map colors are included plus diffuse color setting samples. For Genesis 2 figures in Poser, optimized material presets are also included. The diffuse color samples show how you can easily create your own tints by changing the diffuse color of the hair. Note: For Genesis 2 figures in Poser, this product is compatible via the DSON Importer for Poser
